"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-08-04-pole-vaulter-breaks-silence-penis-costs-chance-olympic-medal-21358332\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"French pole vaulter Anthony Ammirati has spoken out after going viral for the unfortunate end to hisOlympics.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 109, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 6, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.7541201706907629, \"rank\": 0.20119108305999064, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ammirati was hoping to bag a medal in front of his home crowd at the Stade de France but was left disappointed after his penis caused his downfall.\", \"from\": 111, \"to\": 258, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 180, \"end\": 195, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stade de France\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}, {\"begin\": 180, \"end\": 195, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stade de France\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 21-year-old, who won gold in this event at the World Athletics U20 Championships in 2022, looked to have the height to clear 5.70m and take a big step towards the pole vault finalwhen his manhood got in the way.\", \"from\": 260, \"to\": 475, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 311, \"end\": 344, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics_U20_Championships\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"World Athletics U20 Championships\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics_U20_Championships\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics_U20_Championships\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The unfortunate incident effectively ended Ammirati's Olympic hopes, with the Frenchman eventually finishing 12th in Group A with a height of 5.60m.\", \"from\": 477, \"to\": 625, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 594, \"end\": 601, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Group_A\", \"score\": 0.999997322937761, \"rank\": 1.493240556008927e-06, \"text\": \"Group A\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Group_A\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Group_A\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"5.70m was enough for several athletes to advance to the final but Ammirati was denied a place in the showpiece event and admitted he was 'a bit gutted' to miss out.\", \"from\": 627, \"to\": 791, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'It's a big disappointment,' Ammirati said.\", \"from\": 793, \"to\": 836, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I am a bit gutted, because I did not miss anything on the third attempt at 5.70m.\", \"from\": 837, \"to\": 919, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'What I did miss was a bit of jumping in training to fine-tune the settings, just a technical session.\", \"from\": 921, \"to\": 1023, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Anthony Ammirati failed the bar and the commentators are clearly having a hard time acknowledging what happened \\u00f0\\u009f\\u0098\\u0082 HELP I'M DYINGpic.twitter.com/5hOHttVA5g  'I was 100 percent physically, but I was missing a bit of pole vault.\", \"from\": 1025, \"to\": 1253, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The conditions were good.\", \"from\": 1254, \"to\": 1279, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's the first time I have started a competition without any stress.\", \"from\": 1280, \"to\": 1348, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'As I was a total outsider, I only had one goal: to interact with the audience.\", \"from\": 1350, \"to\": 1429, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was almost there.'\", \"from\": 1430, \"to\": 1450, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ENVOL, a pole vault club based in France, sent a message to Ammirati following his Olympics disappointment.\", \"from\": 1452, \"to\": 1559, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1486, \"end\": 1492, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999924230435788, \"rank\": 6.535239328685148e-06, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'A fifteenth place in qualifying for the Paris Olympics with 5m60,' they posted on Instagram.\", \"from\": 1561, \"to\": 1654, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1644, \"end\": 1653, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.14769223890834e-19, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'We are proud of you, even if we are frustrated like you for this bar at 5m70.\", \"from\": 1656, \"to\": 1734, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We wish you an unforgettable Olympic experience.'\", \"from\": 1735, \"to\": 1784, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Fellow French pole vaulter Thibaut Collet also failed to reach the final and said he was 'ashamed' of his performance.\", \"from\": 1786, \"to\": 1904, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1793, \"end\": 1799, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.7541201706907629, \"rank\": 0.20119108305999064, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1813, \"end\": 1820, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anton_Friedrich_Justus_Thibaut\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Thibaut\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anton_Friedrich_Justus_Thibaut\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anton_Friedrich_Justus_Thibaut\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I am extremely ashamed of my performance,' he said.\", \"from\": 1906, \"to\": 1958, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I do not understand: the last few weeks of preparation were too good, we worked really hard.\", \"from\": 1959, \"to\": 2052, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'The hardest thing is to tell yourself that there is nothing I could have done better.'\", \"from\": 2054, \"to\": 2141, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"France's Robin Emig, who suffered the same fate, added: 'I can only blame myself.\", \"from\": 2143, \"to\": 2224, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2143, \"end\": 2149, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999924230435788, \"rank\": 6.535239328685148e-06, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'This competition is like my summer season: I am struggling to find the sensations and to make it happen.'\", \"from\": 2226, \"to\": 2332, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For more stories like this,check our sport page.\", \"from\": 2334, \"to\": 2382, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro Sport for the latest news onFacebook,TwitterandInstagram.\", \"from\": 2384, \"to\": 2454, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:Gold medal winner sleeps in a park after moaning about conditions in the Olympic Village  ArrowMORE:Why do athletes ring the bell in the Stade de France at the Paris 2024 Olympics?\", \"from\": 2456, \"to\": 2646, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:Do you know the Muffin Man?\", \"from\": 2648, \"to\": 2685, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\"